snippet.title: Monster Hunter Wilds World Premiere Trailer at The Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the Monster Hunter Wilds World Premiere Trailer from The Game Awards 2023. Geoff Keighley hosts this global showcase of video games with performances by The Game Awards Orchestra and more, live from Peacock Theater in Los Angeles.
